{"tid":2103644,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美銀報告：資金流入中國基金創5年新高","createTime":"2020-07-11T10:59:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T14:38:14.000Z","uid":51469,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"00aa006d65a9c29c4c79dda592d1111a662fb792","tid":2103644,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T10:59:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537059-20200710.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537059-20200710.htm&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyKQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=1c3bd225\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537059-20200710.htm&h=f67c68c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537059-20200710.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國銀行指出，本周共有61億美元資金流入中國基金，是2015年7月以來新高，亦是歷來第二高。<br />\n<br />\n市場憂慮會重演2015-16年的泡沫，當時滬股在短短數星期內，自高位急挫超過40%。<br />\n<br />\n美銀報告亦顯示，本周有294億美元流入貨幣基金，178億美元流入債券基金，62億美元流入股票基金，24億美元流入黃金基金。"},{"pid":"1a657312765ad44fbb4c3a9b2bd9649f6f8bc1d7","tid":2103644,"uid":167585,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00aa006d65a9c29c4c79dda592d1111a662fb792","tid":2103644,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T10:59:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537059-20200710.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537059-20200710.htm&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyKQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=1c3bd225\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537059-20200710.htm&h=f67c68c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537059-20200710.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國銀行指出，本周共有61億美元資金流入中國基金，是2015年7月以來新高，亦是歷來第二高。<br />\n<br />\n市場憂慮會重演2015-16年的泡沫，當時滬股在短短數星期內，自高位急挫超過40%。<br />\n<br />\n美銀報告亦顯示，本周有294億美元流